These are Puzzles for 5x2 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 5x2-Level-1-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: coffee, mirinda
The people have 2 different jobs:  journalist, firefighter
2 different pets are kept: hedgehog, chinchilla
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: golf, sailing
The people use 2 different means of transport: quad-bike, airplane
1. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the person who's sport is sailing##1
2. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the person driving the airplane##1
3. the firefighter is the owner of the hedgehog##1
4. the journalist is the person drinking coffee##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |     2     |
| Beverage    | coffee       | mirinda  |
| Job         | journalist | firefighter |
| Pet         | chinchilla        | hedgehog     |
| Sport       | sailing     | golf  |
| Transport   | quad-bike    | airplane     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 5x2-Level-1-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: lemonade, mirinda
The people have 2 different jobs:  chef, doctor
2 different pets are kept: fish, frog
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: volleyball, biathlon
The people use 2 different means of transport: quad-bike, bike
1. the doctor is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1
2. the person driving the quad-bike is on the far right##1
3. the owner of the fish is the person who's sport is biathlon##1
4. the owner of the fish is the person drinking mirinda##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |       2       |
| Beverage    | lemonade  | mirinda        |
| Job         | doctor | chef     |
| Pet         | frog  | fish        |
| Sport       | volleyball  | biathlon |
| Transport   | bike      | quad-bike        |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 5x2-Level-1-3::.
There 2 different types of food: nectarine, lemon
The people have 2 different hobbies: magic-tricks, drawing
The people have 2 different jobs:  analyst, architect
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: trance, reggae
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: surfing, basketball
1. the person eating lemon is on the far left##1
2. the fan of reggae is on the right of the analyst##1
3. the fan of trance is on the left of the person who's sport is surfing##1
4. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |         1          |    2     |
| Food          | lemon             | nectarine  |
| Hobby         | drawing         | magic-tricks  |
| Job           | analyst | architect  |
| Music-Genre   | trance         | reggae      |
| Sport         | basketball      | surfing |

