The people prefer 2 different types of sport: baseball, biathlon
1. the person who's hobby is drawing is the person who's sport is biathlon##1
2. the person drinking tea is on the far right##1
3. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the left of the person watching romance movies##1
4. the fan of d&b is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |
| Beverage      | hot-chocolate        | tea       |
| Hobby         | drawing  | hiking |
| Movie-Genre   | action     | romance    |
| Music-Genre   | d&b     | dubstep      |
| Sport         | biathlon | baseball     |

