.:: Puzzle 5x2-Level-1-20::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: video-games, writing
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: fantasy, animation
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: d&b, ambient
2 different pets are kept: lizard, chinchilla
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: golf, basketball
1. the fan of ambient is on the left of the person watching fantasy movies##1
2. the person who's sport is golf is the person who's hobby is writing##1
3. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left of the person who's hobby is writing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |
| Hobby         | video-games     | writing |
| Movie-Genre   | animation | fantasy   |
| Music-Genre   | ambient      | d&b |
| Pet           | chinchilla         | lizard     |
| Sport         | basketball  | golf |

 